    - SAUCE: (noup) Update spl to 0.6.5.10-1, zfs to 0.6.5.10-1ubuntu2
    - snapcraft.yaml: Sync with xenial
    - [Config] CONFIG_CAVIUM_ERRATUM_30115=y

